des: "So many favorite flavors and ingredients--pasta, tomato, Cheddar cheese, ground beef--are in this one easy skillet supper."
ins:

Add soups, water and pasta.  Heat to a boil.  Cook over medium heat 10 minutes or until done, stirring often.
